Package: PRmixer
Title: An R package to help distributing students for peer review activities
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Florencia",
           family = "D'Andrea",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "florencia.dandrea@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0041-097X"))
Description: This package allows students to be randomized into groups of different sizes as reviewers of another group. The function considers that: (1) Students cannot be assigned as reviewers of the same group, (2) All groups must have reviewers.
